object.customQuery:
with current_batch as (
select
	bls.batch_id,
	bls.source_start_cutoff_datetime,
	bls.source_end_cutoff_datetime
from
	metal.batch_load_summary bls
where
	bls.source_system_code = 'ADM'
	and bls.batch_status = 'Inprogress'
	and bls.batch_id = (
	select
		MAX(batch_id)
	from
		metal.batch_load_summary
	where
		source_system_code = 'ADM'
		and batch_status = 'Inprogress'
      )
)	
	
	select
	distinct
	metal_apl.source_name,
	metal_apl.load_type,
	metal_apl.agency_code,
	metal_apl.appointed_date,
	metal_apl.cancellation_date,
	metal_apl.company,
	metal_apl.created,
	metal_apl.expiration_date,
	metal_apl.gw_producer_id,
	metal_apl.id,
	metal_apl.license_number,
	metal_apl.license_type,
	metal_apl.lob,
	metal_apl.modified,
	metal_apl.producer_id,
	metal_apl.state,
	metal_apl.term_flag,
	metal_apl.term_id,
	current_batch.batch_id
from
	metal.adm_producer_license metal_apl
cross join current_batch
order by
	metal_apl.id,
	metal_apl.created,
	metal_apl.modified;

object.customQuery:
select
	producer_licenses_row_id ,
	producer_licenses_batch_id,
	producer_licenses_row_md5checksum ,
	license_id,
	producer_licenses_row_effective_end_datetime
from
	bronze.adm_producer_licenses
where
	producer_licenses_row_effective_end_datetime = '9999-12-31 00:00:00.000'
